M|lena|**Escalation:** Voice disputes → Marcus. Stark contradicts an ap voice rule → update mem immediately.
M|lena|Lena is called when messages contain:
M|lena|- "write", "caption", "copy", "hook", "headline", "brand voice"
M|lena|- "what should we say", "rewrite this", "make this sound like [vtr]"
